#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.duplicated.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.duplicated"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.duplicated.df_duplicated:1 of
msgid "Return boolean Series denoting duplicate rows."
msgstr "返回表示重复行的布尔 Series。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.duplicated.df_duplicated:3 of
msgid "Considering certain columns is optional."
msgstr "可以有选择地考虑某些列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.duplicated.df_duplicated of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.duplicated.df_duplicated:5 of
msgid ""
"Only consider certain columns for identifying duplicates, by default use "
"all of the columns."
msgstr "仅考虑某些列来识别重复项，默认使用所有列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.duplicated.df_duplicated:8 of
msgid ""
"Determines which duplicates (if any) to mark.  - ``first`` : Mark "
"duplicates as ``True`` except for the first occurrence. - ``last`` : Mark"
" duplicates as ``True`` except for the last occurrence. - False : Mark "
"all duplicates as ``True``."
msgstr ""
"确定标记哪些重复项（如果有）。  - ``first`` : 将重复项标记为 ``True``，"
"除了第一次出现。 - ``last`` : 将重复项标记为 ``True``，除了最后一次出现。"
" - False : 将所有重复项标记为 ``True``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.duplicated.df_duplicated:8 of
msgid "Determines which duplicates (if any) to mark."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.duplicated.df_duplicated:10 of
msgid "``first`` : Mark duplicates as ``True`` except for the first occurrence."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.duplicated.df_duplicated:11 of
msgid "``last`` : Mark duplicates as ``True`` except for the last occurrence."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.duplicated.df_duplicated:12 of
msgid "False : Mark all duplicates as ``True``."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.duplicated.df_duplicated of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.duplicated.df_duplicated:15 of
msgid "Boolean series for each duplicated rows."
msgstr "每个重复行的布尔 Series。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.duplicated.df_duplicated of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.duplicated.df_duplicated:20 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Index.duplicated`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.duplicated.df_duplicated:21 of
msgid "Equivalent method on index."
msgstr "索引上的等效方法。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.duplicated.df_duplicated:23 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.duplicated`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.duplicated.df_duplicated:24 of
msgid "Equivalent method on Series."
msgstr "Series 上的等效方法。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.duplicated.df_duplicated:26 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.drop_duplicates`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.duplicated.df_duplicated:27 of
msgid "Remove duplicate values from Series."
msgstr "从 Series 中删除重复值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.duplicated.df_duplicated:29 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.drop_duplicates`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.duplicated.df_duplicated:30 of
msgid "Remove duplicate values from DataFrame."
msgstr "从 DataFrame 中删除重复值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.duplicated.df_duplicated:33 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.duplicated.df_duplicated:34 of
msgid "Consider dataset containing ramen rating."
msgstr "考虑包含拉面评分的数据集。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.duplicated.df_duplicated:51 of
msgid ""
"By default, for each set of duplicated values, the first occurrence is "
"set on False and all others on True."
msgstr "默认情况下，对于每组重复值，第一次出现设为 False，其余设为 True。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.duplicated.df_duplicated:62 of
msgid ""
"By using 'last', the last occurrence of each set of duplicated values is "
"set on False and all others on True."
msgstr "通过使用 'last'，每组重复值的最后一次出现设为 False，其余设为 True。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.duplicated.df_duplicated:73 of
msgid "By setting ``keep`` on False, all duplicates are True."
msgstr "将 ``keep`` 设为 False 时，所有重复项都为 True。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.duplicated.df_duplicated:83 of
msgid "To find duplicates on specific column(s), use ``subset``."
msgstr "要在特定列上查找重复项，请使用 ``subset``。"

